<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c2">(١٩)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَلَا يَسْتَحْسِرُونَ}</span> ... لَا يَمَلُّونَ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(٢٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{لَا يَفْتُرُونَ}</span> ... لَا يَضْعُفُونَ، وَلَا يَسْأَمُونَ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(٢١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{هُمْ يُنشِرُونَ}</span> ... هُمْ يُحْيُونَ المَوْتَى؟ كَلَّا!<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(٢٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{إِلَّا اللَّهُ لَفَسَدَتَا}</span> ... غَيْرُ اللهِ لَاخْتَلَّ نِظَامُهُمَا، وخَرِبَتَا؛ لِحُصُولِ التَّنَازُع.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(٢٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{فَسُبْحَانَ اللَّهِ}</span> ... تَنَزَّهَ، وَتَقَدَّسَ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(٢٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{ذِكْرُ مَن مَّعِيَ}</span> ... القُرْآنُ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(٢٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَذِكْرُ مَن قَبْلِي}</span> ... الكُتُبُ السَّابِقَةُ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c2">(٣٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{رَتْقًا}</span> ... مُلْتَصِقَتَيْنِ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c2">(٣٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{فَفَتَقْنَاهُمَا}</span> ... فَفَصَلْنَاهُمَا بِقُدْرَتِنَا.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c2">(٣١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{رَوَاسِيَ}</span> ... جِبَالًا تُثَبِّتُهَا.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c2">(٣١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{أَن تَمِيدَ}</span> ... لِئَلَّا تَضْطَرِبَ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c2">(٣١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{فِجَاجًا سُبُلًا}</span> ... طُرُقًا وَاسِعَةً مَسْلْوكَةً.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c2">(٣٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{سَقْفًا مَّحْفُوظًا}</span> ... لَا تَسْقُطُ، وَلَا تَخْتَرِقُهَا الشَّيَاطِينُ.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span class="c2">(٣٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{فِي فَلَكٍ يَسْبَحُونَ}</span> ... فِي مَدَارٍ يَجْرِي فِيهِ لَا يَحِيدُ عَنْهُ.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span><span class="c2">(٣٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَنَبْلُوكُم}</span> ... نَخْتَبِرُكُمْ مَعَ عِلْمِنَا بِحَالِكُمْ.<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span><span class="c2">(٣٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{يَذْكُرُ آلِهَتَكُمْ}</span> ... يَعِيبُهَا.<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>